      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive preservation. Maintained to an exacting standard, this vehicle remains in pristine condition, exhibiting flawless aesthetic and mechanical integrity. Having been stored in a climate-controlled environment, it offers the discerning buyer a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade specimen that transcends the typical market offering.",
      "price": 48200.0,
